txt.en: 'We've seen Corsair flags on the top of Emyn Ernil. I believe they have scaled the sides of the mountain and somehow found a way in through some cracks and open air caves.\n\n'If they are down there they are surely exploring and mapping the tunnels. Search the tunnels and find any Corsair surveyors. Make sure their information doesn't get back to their ships.'
Corsairs have been exploring and scouting the tunnels beneath Emyn Ernil.
'We don't know the full extent of the tunnels yet ourselves. Until we do, the Corsairs cannot have that information.'
The Corsair surveyors are exploring the tunnels beneath Emyn Ernil.\n\nGelloth asked you to prevent the Corsair surveyors from exploring and mapping the tunnels beneath Emyn Ernil.
Gelloth can be found in Dol Amroth.\n\nGelloth will be very pleased to hear the surveyors have been eliminated.
